{{vgname|荒野八人组|en=The Wild Eight|aka=荒野八侠}}是一款自由度高的[[生存模拟游戏|模拟生存类游戏]]。游戏程序由俄罗斯公司Fntastic开发，HypeTrain Digital出版。玩家将扮演一名在空难中幸存，却又身处于阿拉斯加丛林深处的角色。为了活下去，玩家必须学会合作克服一系列的困难。Fntastic已于2016年5月赢得了一笔来自[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]的资金作为初始研发经费。<ref name="KS">Fntastic (May 14, 2016). </ref>

试玩版于2016年5月23日通过 Game Jolt 平台发布，<ref name="gamejolt">{{Cite web |url=http://gamejolt.com/games/the-wild-eight/150978 |title="The Wild Eight by Fntastic on Game Jolt" |accessdate=2016-08-31 |archive-date=2016-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160901053306/http://gamejolt.com/games/the-wild-eight/150978 |dead-url=no }}</ref>尽管这只包括了部分游戏内容，但仍可以借此窥见开发者的思路与游戏的基本框架，比如资源系统、温饱系统、属性升级、建筑、制造等内容。<ref name="pcgamerdemo">[http://www.pcgamer.com/the-wild-eight-now-has-a-free-pre-alpha-demo/ "The Wild Eight now has a free, 'pre-alpha' demo"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-wild-eight-now-has-a-free-pre-alpha-demo/ |date=20160827050304 }}.</ref><ref name="eurogamerdemo">{{Cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-04-06-introducing-procedurally-generated-co-op-survival-sim-the-wild-eight |title="Introducing procedurally-generated co-op survival sim The Wild Eight" |accessdate=2016-08-31 |archive-date=2016-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824012931/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-04-06-introducing-procedurally-generated-co-op-survival-sim-the-wild-eight |dead-url=no }}</ref>

完整版预计将于2016年秋登陆[[Steam|Steam]]平台与主机平台。<ref name="website">{{Cite web |url=http://thewildeight.com/ |title="The Wild Eight – Official Website" |accessdate=2016-08-31 |archive-date=2016-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160906021400/http://thewildeight.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 简介 ==

开发者从《[[暗黑破坏神|暗黑破坏神]]》、《[[饥荒|饥荒]]》等游戏中获得灵感，结合自身在俄罗斯[[雅库特|雅库特]]地区的生活经验创作了这款游戏。《荒野八人组》的故事建立在一个八人小组飞机失事后荒野生还的基础之上，他们为了生存，必须合作克服重重障碍。<ref name="vg247news">[https://www.vg247.com/2016/05/02/co-op-survival-game-the-wild-eight-hits-kickstarter-goal-of-50000 "Co-op survival game The Wild Eight hits Kickstarter goal of $50,000"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.vg247.com/2016/05/02/co-op-survival-game-the-wild-eight-hits-kickstarter-goal-of-50000 |date=20160927201547 }}. [[VG247|vg247]]</ref>在这个过程中，幸存者们的生命无时无刻被无情的自然威胁着。根据官方网站的介绍，玩家必须发展一系列的生存技能以抵御残酷的环境，比方说砍柴以点亮篝火维持适当的温度，制作武器来防御侵略，狩猎等等。<ref name="pcgamerannouncement">{{Cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-wild-eight-is-co-op-survival-with-mutated-wolves |title="The Wild Eight is co-op survival with mutated wolves" |accessdate=2016-08-31 |archive-date=2016-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813014643/http://www.pcgamer.com/the-wild-eight-is-co-op-survival-with-mutated-wolves/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

游戏也将支持单人模式。完整版将有更佳丰富的单人与多人内容。

== 发展历程 ==

这是来自[[萨哈共和国|萨哈共和国]]的Fntastic团队的第一部原创大作。<ref name="rockpapernews">[https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2016/04/28/co-op-survival-game/ "Co-op survival game The Wild Eight"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2016/04/28/co-op-survival-game/ |date=20160429120542 }}.</ref>团队已赢得了来自[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]公司的一笔五万美元的初始研发投入。<ref name="vg247news" />同时也通过Indiegogo公司提供的平台发起众筹，截止2016年8月，项目总经费已超过六万美元。<ref name="indiegogo">[https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/the-wild-eight-game-rpg# "The Wild Eight on Indiegogo"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/the-wild-eight-game-rpg |date=20160827200139 }}. indiegogo</ref>

